      <title>中国对欧投资缩减，主要投向电动汽车行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/chinese-investment-in-europe-shrinks-mostly-goes-to-ev-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，中国企业对欧洲的投资降至十多年来的最低水平，大部分新资金流入电动汽车和相关行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/chinese-investment-in-europe-shrinks-mostly-goes-to-ev-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 02:40:35 GMT</pubDate>
